          "content": "## Working Capital\nDifference between current assets and liabilities.\n\n### Components\n- Cash\n- Inventory\n- Receivables\n\n### Importance\nEnsures liquidity.",
          "examples": ["Daily business expenses", "Inventory stock"],
          "common_mistakes": [
